<h1>Introduction</h1>

<p>The @@@D2Lightning@@@ Sorceress is the fastest Chaos Sanctuary clearing character in the game, known for her extremely high Damage output and mobility. While fragile, when you pair this Sorceress up with an @@@D2Infinity@@@ Mercenary there are very few places she cannot clear quickly.</p>

<h1>Quick Reference</h1>

<h2>Skill Build</h2>

<p>The following section shows the core skills for the @@@D2Lightning@@@ Sorceress. For a detailed breakdown of all core and optional skills as well as the recommended order for allocating skill points, refer to the Skills section of this guide.</p>

<ol>
<li>1 point to all prerequisites</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2Lightning@@@ - Max first, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2ChainLightning@@@ - Max after Lightning, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2LightningMastery@@@ - Max after @@@D2ChainLightning@@@, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2ChargedBolt@@@ - Max after @@@D2LightningMastery@@@, required</li>
<li>20 points to @@@D2Nova@@@ - Max after @@@D2ChargedBolt@@@, required</li>
<li>1 points to @@@D2Teleport@@@ - Skill right at level 18, required</li>
</ol>

